                              OWLOntologyCreationException,

        Static convenience method which: (1) creates an Obo2Owl bridge object (2) parses an obo file from a URL (3) converts that to an OWL ontology (4) saves the OWL ontology as RDF/XML.
        Parameters:
        iri - the iri
        outFile - the out file
        manager - manager to use
        Throws:
        IOException - Signals that an I/O exception has occurred.
        OWLOntologyCreationException - the oWL ontology creation exception
        OWLOntologyStorageException - the oWL ontology storage exception
        OBOFormatParserException - the oBO format parser exception
